rfect there, but it is quite rapid to work this way. It can be easily re-factored later too. As you can see, I setup every steps in order. In that example, string are not yet localized, but we can leverage of .Net Resource file easily by having all steps in the ViewModel. The selector require to use ", mdx("strong", {
